          <td colspan="2" valign="top" class="titulo2">An  excerpt from &#8220;The Nightingales  of Troy&#8221; <a href="../../issue4/alice_fulton/bio.php" class="link3">by Alice Fulton</a></span></td>
          <td>&nbsp;</td>
